import React from "react";
export default class App extends React.Component {
   render() {
      return <Navbar brand={<a />} alignLinks="right">
<Button node="a">
button
</Button>
<Button node="a">
button

cloud
</Icon>
</Button>
<Button node="a" large>
large button
</Button>
</Navbar>
   }
}
